    {
        "type": "twitter",
        "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
        "timestamp": "ch3",
        "content": {
            "text": "i don't usually do threads but i need to say this",
            "tags": [
                "willmackisreal"
            ]
        },
        "stats": {
            "likes": 7382,
            "retweets": 1076,
            "quote_retweets": 522
        },
        "replies": [
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "seeing two nhl players just… exist openly and say they're in love? i can't even explain what that did to me."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 325,
                    "retweets": 44,
                    "answers": 21
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "when i was a kid playing hockey, you learned *real* fast what was okay and what wasn't. and being anything other than straight? yeah. that wasn't even something you said out loud."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 218,
                    "retweets": 41,
                    "answers": 28
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "i remember being in locker rooms where people would joke about it, throw words around like it was nothing. and you just laugh along because what else are you gonna do?"
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 245,
                    "retweets": 41,
                    "answers": 21
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "so you get good at hiding. like REALLY good."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 60,
                    "retweets": 7,
                    "answers": 3
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "you change how you talk. how you react. you don't look too long, don't say too much, don't be “suspect.” you just try to survive it."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 247,
                    "retweets": 29,
                    "answers": 11
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "and the thing is… you start to believe that there's no place for you in the game if you're honest about who you are."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 91,
                    "retweets": 13,
                    "answers": 2
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "i quit before i ever found out if i could've made it anywhere. not because i didn't love hockey, but because i didn't think hockey could ever love me back."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 80,
                    "retweets": 7,
                    "answers": 8
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "so yeah. seeing this now? two guys in the league just saying “this is who we are” and not apologizing for it?"
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 38,
                    "retweets": 7,
                    "answers": 3
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "it matters more than people realize."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 41,
                    "retweets": 3,
                    "answers": 6
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "there's some kid somewhere right now, sitting in a freezing rink, lacing up their skates, feeling like they have to hide every part of themselves…"
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 236,
                    "retweets": 13,
                    "answers": 11
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "and today, maybe for the first time, they're thinking: “maybe i don't have to.”"
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 61,
                    "retweets": 11,
                    "answers": 4
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "that's everything."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 144,
                    "retweets": 28,
                    "answers": 10
                }
            },
            {
                "author": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "replyingto": "EmotionallyOffside",
                "content": {
                    "text": "i don't know those players. they don't know me. but what they did? it reached people like me. it reached *far*."
                },
                "stats": {
                    "likes": 329,
                    "retweets": 55,
                    "answers": 8
                }
            },
            {
